    "This significantly limited the model's ability to focus capacity where needed.",
    "Accuracy dropped by 3.5We observed slower convergence during training and higher evaluation loss compared to DRaFT-Q.",
    "Static ranks distribute representational power uniformly, which is inefficient for tasks with uneven token importance or variable depth of reasoning.",
    "The dynamic allocator, driven by EMA of curvature, adjusts ranks to match task demands -increasing rank in early transformer blocks for shallow QA tasks and deeper layers for multi-hop reasoning.",
